OL,5, A mother of two said she only makes #2 
OL,6, a day when she works overtime due to   
OL,7, the rising cost of childcare fees.     
OL,9,FLouise Morgan, from Swansea, wants to  
OL,10,Fwork more hours to advance her career, 
